copyEntities

void copyEntities(Account from,
                  Account to)
                  throws IOException,
                         IllegalAccessException
Copy all entities from one account to another. Overwrites existing entities in target account if they already exist. This operation is not atomic, and should be used only in specific circumstances, such as when bootstrapping a new, empty account.

Parameters:
from - Account to copy from
to - Account to copy to
Throws:
IOException - if there was a problem copying the entities
IllegalAccessException
